Nagios-Plugin-IMAPQuota version 0.01
====================================

This is a plugin for Nagios, which allows you to monitor a single
IMAP mailbox for quota usage, provided that your mail server supports it.

After installing this module, use the check_imap_quota.pl script as the Nagios plugin.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Mail::IMAPClient
  Nagios::Plugin

